_aChangeLog.text: Tunnels have been Vastly improved. Deleted the old godawful models, and replaced them with newer, better looking and more functioning ones.
Radar minimap now available on top left corner
Hint/Skip have been added for optimization
All files are neatly packed in single .bsp, instead of multiple files, just plug and play!
Lights in tunnels have also been improved
removed blasters, now you can destroy signs with just your pistols

_sText:
Now presenting 3rd map in the wintermaze_2016 series with added underground tunnel system.
See the video above for map tour. 

Player count: 20vs20

If you have anny suggestions, ideas or bug reports, please let me know. 

Hope you enjoy the map :)
